        "summary": "Governor of Bihar, Lieutenant General (Retired) Syed Ata Hasnain and Minister of State for External Affairs Pabitra Margherita will visit Iran today to attend the funeral ceremony of the late Supreme Leader of Iran, Grand Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei. The Ministry of External Affairs said the high-level representation in the ceremony underscores the importance of […]",
