        "title": "India steps up humanitarian assistance to earthquake-hit Venezuela under Operation Amistad",
        "summary": "India has stepped up its humanitarian assistance to earthquake-hit Venezuela under Operation Amistad. Sharing pictures of the ongoing medical relief efforts on social media, the Ministry of External Affairs said that the Army Field Hospital continues to provide medical care to affected communities in Venezuela. The Indian Embassy in Venezuela has said that India’s humanitarian […]",
        "article": "India has stepped up its humanitarian assistance to earthquake-hit Venezuela under Operation Amistad. Sharing pictures of the ongoing medical relief efforts on social media, the Ministry of External Affairs said that the Army Field Hospital continues to provide medical care to affected communities in Venezuela. The Indian Embassy in Venezuela has said that India’s humanitarian relief efforts in the South American nation have received widespread acclaim from the public for its professionalism and quality of service.",
