        "title": "Dept of Youth Affairs organises Industry Association Conclave of MY Bharat in New Delhi",
        "summary": "The Department of Youth Affairs today organised an Industry Association Conclave of MY Bharat in New Delhi. Leading industry bodies, including ASSOCHAM, FICCI, CAIT and CII, participated in the conclave. The event aimed to introduce the MY Bharat ecosystem to industry stakeholders and invite industry associations, corporates and public sector undertakings to join the initiative. […]",
        "article": "The Department of Youth Affairs today organised an Industry Association Conclave of MY Bharat in New Delhi. Leading industry bodies, including ASSOCHAM, FICCI, CAIT and CII, participated in the conclave. The event aimed to introduce the MY Bharat ecosystem to industry stakeholders and invite industry associations, corporates and public sector undertakings to join the initiative. The conclave also focused on exploring frameworks for future collaboration on youth development and aligning national youth goals with industry-led initiatives. Speaking on the occasion, Union Minister for Youth Affairs and Sports, Dr Mansukh Mandaviya, said that the youth of the country are the key drivers in realising the vision of a Viksit Bharat by 2047. He said that collaboration between industry and MY Bharat will help channel this youth energy towards national development goals.",
