        "title": "Japan’s PM Sanae Takaichi departs from India after concluding successful visit",
        "summary": "Prime Minister of Japan, Sanae Takaichi, has departed from India following her highly successful visit. Ms Takaichi was seen off by Minister of State Dr Jitendra Singh. During her visit, she attended the 16th India-Japan Annual Summit in New Delhi. In a social media post, the External Affairs Ministry said that the visit reaffirmed the […]",
        "article": "Prime Minister of Japan, Sanae Takaichi, has departed from India following her highly successful visit. Ms Takaichi was seen off by Minister of State Dr Jitendra Singh. During her visit, she attended the 16th India-Japan Annual Summit in New Delhi. In a social media post, the External Affairs Ministry said that the visit reaffirmed the commitment of both sides to nurture a partnership pivotal to the shared growth and prosperity of both countries and an anchor for promoting peace, prosperity and stability in the Indo-Pacific and beyond.",
