        "summary": "India has sought a thorough investigation by the Venezuelan authorities into the desecration and removal of organs from the mortal remains of late seafarer Rakesh Chauhan. In a social media post, the Indian Embassy in Caracas said that the Mission has been pursuing the matter with the concerned local authorities since the incident came to […]",
        "article": "India has sought a thorough investigation by the Venezuelan authorities into the desecration and removal of organs from the mortal remains of late seafarer Rakesh Chauhan. In a social media post, the Indian Embassy in Caracas said that the Mission has been pursuing the matter with the concerned local authorities since the incident came to light.",
