        "title": "Thailand: Nine monks killed after 11-year-old boy crashes pickup truck into pilgrimage group",
        "summary": "In Thailand, nine monks were killed yesterday when an 11-year-old boy crashed a pickup truck into a group of monks on a pilgrimage walk in northeastern Mukdahan province. Officials said a total of 35 monks from Mukdahan province were on the pilgrimage. Five monks were killed at the scene, while four others died at a […]",
        "article": "In Thailand, nine monks were killed yesterday when an 11-year-old boy crashed a pickup truck into a group of monks on a pilgrimage walk in northeastern Mukdahan province. Officials said a total of 35 monks from Mukdahan province were on the pilgrimage. Five monks were killed at the scene, while four others died at a hospital. Thirteen others were hospitalised, three of whom are in critical condition. Police said the boy is in custody and will be questioned upon the arrival of state child protection officers. The cause of the accident is under investigation.",
